exciting perspectives to enhance your gameplay experience.\n\n\ud83c\udfe0 **GAME MODES\ud83c\udfe0**\n\nHave fun and talk with other bricks in our casual mode or show your inner brick and jump into an infection lobby. More game modes soon to come..\n\n\u2757\ufe0f\u2757\ufe0f**BIG UPDATES CONSTANTLY\u2757\ufe0f\u2757\ufe0f**\n\nWe do our best to get out updates every week or every other week to best support our community. We built what the community wants!\n\n\n\ud83c\udfc0 **SHOOT HOOPS LIKE NEVER BEFORE** \ud83c\udfc0 \n\nHit the basketball court for some epic trick shots. Whether you\u2019re a baller or just want hit some jumpers, the court is yours.\n\n\n\n\n\ud83d\udecd\ufe0f **EXPLORE THE MALL AND GET COSMETICS \ud83d\udecd\ufe0f**\n\nVisit our in-game mall and deck out your brick with an array of cosmetics. From funky outfits to stylish accessories, there\u2019s something for everyone.\n\n\ud83e\udd73 **JOIN THE BRICK MANIA NOW \ud83e\udd73**\n\nReady to experience life as a brick? Join the Brick Mania now and embark on a tiny, yet massive adventure. Play for free and let the fun begin! Join our Discord to get support or find people to play with: https://discord.gg/brickmania", "short_description": "Step into the shoes of a miniature, brick in a room-sized adventure.Run, Jump, Tag, Shoot hoops, Explore mods, take videos using in game camera mod, and customize your look at the in-game mall."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.gotmotion.gg/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Got Motion", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://gotmotion.gg/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "interne